## Responsive Considerations

All examples should scale down shadows/borders on mobile:

```css
:root {
  --shadow: 3px 3px 0 #000;
  --border: 2px;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  :root {
    --shadow: 4px 4px 0 #000;
    --border: 3px;
  }
}

@media (min-width: 1024px) {
  :root {
    --shadow: 6px 6px 0 #000;
    --border: 4px;
  }
}
```

